data.description: Show and Sell this very nice property that's located in a Great area of Gardena on a quiet cud de sac street. It's perfect for first time home buyers just starting out. Or it's for anyone just looking for a very nice property in this Great sought after area of Gardena in the beautiful Holly Park. It has hardwood floors, central heat and air, copper plumbing, built ins in the kitchen, a covered patio, four fruit tress located in a nice cozy back yard and more. FYI, A Current Popular TV Judge once lived and grew up on this very Street of the property. It Will Not Last! So Please call the Listing Broker/Agent Today to make your appointment. See you in Escrow!!!
